# Funcin para calcular media y desviacin estndar
def mean_std(series):
    return f"{series.mean():.1f}  {series.std():.1f}"

 
# Funcin para calcular el porcentaje para variables categricas
def category_percentage(series):
    counts = series.value_counts(normalize=True) * 100
    # Redondear y convertir todos los porcentajes a string
    percentages = [f"{p:.0f}" for p in counts]

    num_unique_classes = series.nunique(dropna=True)
    if len(percentages) < num_unique_classes:
        percentages += ["0"] * (num_unique_classes - len(percentages))
    # Unir los porcentajes con "/"
    return "/".join(percentages)



numeric_vars = ['Age', 'BMI', 'AlcoholConsumption', 'PhysicalActivity', 'DietQuality', 'SleepQuality',
               'SystolicBP', 'DiastolicBP', 'CholesterolTotal', 'CholesterolLDL', 'CholesterolHDL', 
               'CholesterolTriglycerides', 'MMSE', 'FunctionalAssessment', 'ADL']

categorical_vars = ['Gender', 'Ethnicity', 'EducationLevel', 'Smoking', 'FamilyHistoryAlzheimers', 
                    'CardiovascularDisease', 'Diabetes', 'Depression', 'HeadInjury', 'Hypertension',
                   'MemoryComplaints', 'BehavioralProblems', 'Confusion', 'Disorientation', 'PersonalityChanges',
                   'DifficultyCompletingTasks', 'Forgetfulness']



results = []


for var in df:
    if var in numeric_vars:
        total = mean_std(df[var])
        sano = mean_std(df[df['Diagnosis'] == 0][var])
        alzheimer = mean_std(df[df['Diagnosis'] == 1][var])
    else:  # Categricas
        total = category_percentage(df[var])
        sano = category_percentage(df[df['Diagnosis'] == 0][var])
        alzheimer = category_percentage(df[df['Diagnosis'] == 1][var])
    
    results.append({
        'Variable': var,
        'Total': total,
        'Sano': sano,
        'Alzheimer': alzheimer
    })

def analyze_differences(data, target_column):
    results = []

    for var in data.columns:
        if var == target_column:
            continue
        
        grupo0 = data[data[target_column] == 0][var].dropna()
        grupo1 = data[data[target_column] == 1][var].dropna()

        # Variables categricas
        if data[var].dtype == 'object' or data[var].nunique() < 10:
            contingency_table = pd.crosstab(data[var], data[target_column])
            if contingency_table.values.min() < 5:
                # Usar el test de Fisher si hay valores pequeos
                odds_ratio, p_value = fisher_exact(contingency_table)
                test = 'Fisher exact test'
            else:
                chi2, p_value, dof, expected = chi2_contingency(contingency_table)
                test = 'Chi-squared test'
            results.append((var, test, p_value*31, p_value*31 < 0.05))
        
        # Variables numricas
        else:
            # Test de normalidad
            stat0, p_shapiro0 = shapiro(grupo0)
            stat1, p_shapiro1 = shapiro(grupo1)

            normal0 = p_shapiro0 > 0.05
            normal1 = p_shapiro1 > 0.05

            if normal0 and normal1:
                # Test paramtrico
                stat, p_value = ttest_ind(grupo0, grupo1)
                test = 't-test'
            else:
                # Test no paramtrico
                stat, p_value = mannwhitneyu(grupo0, grupo1)
                test = 'Mann-Whitney U test'
            results.append((var, test, p_value*31, p_value*31 < 0.05)) # Correccion de Bonferroni

    results_df = pd.DataFrame(results, columns=['Variable', 'Test usado', 'Valor p', '*'])
    return results_df

    axes[j].set_title(var, fontsize=14)
    axes[j].set_xlabel('', fontsize=12)
    axes[j].set_ylabel('Proporcin', fontsize=12)
    axes[j].set_xticklabels(['Controles', 'Alzheimer'])
    

sns.despine()
plt.tight_layout(w_pad=6)

In [28]:
def plot_roc_curve(y_test, y_probs, model_name):
    
    fpr, tpr, _ = roc_curve(y_test, y_probs)
    
    roc_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred)
    
    # Grfica
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))
    plt.plot(fpr, tpr, color='blue', lw=2, label=f'ROC curve (AUC = {roc_auc:.2f})')
    plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], 'k--', lw=2)
    plt.xlim([0.0, 1.0])
    plt.ylim([0.0, 1.05])
    plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')
    plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')
    plt.title(f'Receiver Operating Characteristic - {model_name}')
    plt.legend(loc="lower right")
    plt.show()
    
    return roc_auc

plt.hlines(
    y=df_plot['Feature'],
    xmin=0,
    xmax=df_plot['Importance'],
    color='darkblue',
    linewidth=1)

plt.plot(
    df_plot['Importance'],
    df_plot['Feature'],
    'o',
    markersize=4,
    color='darkblue')

plt.xlabel('Importancia', fontsize=10)
plt.xlim(0, 26)
plt.xticks(fontsize=9)
plt.yticks(fontsize=9)
plt.tick_params(axis='y', which='major', pad=10)
sns.despine()

plt.grid(False)
plt.tight_layout()

# Guardar como PNG
plt.savefig("./Figuras/variables_riskfactors.png", dpi=500)

plt.show()
